<h2 id="asking-a-data-science-question">Asking a data science question</h2>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>What is the question you are trying to answer ?</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>What steps or tools did you use to answer it?</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>what did you expect to see?</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>What did you see instead?</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>what other solutions have you thought about?</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>What is your system info</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><a href="https://www.coursera.org/learn/data-scientists-tools/lecture/KPkZz/getting-help">Coursera course on data sceince</a></p>

